gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 123, Spurs 118
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Spurs, 123-118. LeBron James recorded 30 points, nine assists, and seven rebounds for the Lakers, with Anthony Davis adding 28 points and 13 rebounds in the victory. Victor Wembanyama tallied 27 points, 10 rebounds, eight assists, five blocks, and five steals for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 31-27, while the Spurs fall to 11-46.
